data.description: Price Improvement! Half acre plus lot in prime Scottsdale location in the most coveted 85254 Zip Code with a 5 Bdrm 3.5 Bath Residence with beautiful curb appeal and a large circular drive! Garage parking for 6 plus cars includes a Standard two car garage plus a four and a half car climate controlled garage/workshop. If that isn't enough there is room for all of your toys w/two large RV Pads including RV Hook Up. If you have a Boat...there is room, RV...there is room, Quads/Jet Skis...there is room.  Enjoy your resort style backyard with diving pool, grass area,  and a gazebo that screams entertainment! Add a solar system for greatly reduced bills and put this all 5 minutes away from Kierland and the Scottsdale Quarter! It doesn't get much better than this!
